-- Unicredit Unit Yapi Kredi to Sponsor UEFA Champions League
-- B y   E r c a n   E r s o y
-- 2012-08-17T14:25:33Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-17/unicredit-unit-yapi-kredi-to-sponsor-uefa-champions-league.html
Yapi Kredi Bankasi AS, a Turkish
lender co-owned by  Unicredit SpA (UCG)  and  Koc Holding AS (KCHOL)  of  Turkey ,
will sponsor UEFA Champions League for three years as the
tournament’s official bank, chief executive Faik Acikalin said.  Yapi Kredi is the first Turkish bank to sponsor the soccer
tournament, Acikalin said in an e-mailed statement. He didn’t
give a value for the sponsorship.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ercan Ersoy in Istanbul at 
 eersoy@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Benedikt Kammel at 
 bkammel@bloomberg.net  